data.text:
1966 (The Deadly Bees; Gamera Vs. Barugon; Godzilla Vs. the Sea Monster; Manos, the Hands of Fate; The Projected Man; Secret Agent Super Dragon; The Wild, Wild World of Batwoman.)

01/08 Lloyd Whitlock (age 75), who played Capt. Clinton in the season four serial UNDERSEA KINGDOM.

02/03 Herbert J. Yates (age 85), producer of the season four serial UNDERSEA KINGDOM.

02/16 Don Rowan (age 61), who played a guardsman in the season four serial UNDERSEA KINGDOM.

02/26 Minerva Urecal (age 71), who played Fagah in the movie in episode 105- THE CORPSE VANISHES.

03/07 Chief Yowlachie (age 74), who played Bald Eagle in the movie in episode 510- THE PAINTED HILLS.

03/08 Ken Terrell (age 61), who played Joe Marcella in the movie in episode 409- THE INDESTRUCTIBLE MAN and a henchman in the season one serial RADAR MEN FROM THE MOON.

03/19 Tom Lambert (age 72), sound engineer for the movie in episode 201- ROCKETSHIP X-M.

03/21 Franco Lolli (age 55), art director for the movie in episode 412- HERCULES AND THE CAPTIVE WOMEN.

03/22 Everett Glass (age 75), who played Timmek in the movie WORLD WITHOUT END, riffed in MST3K's first live show.

04/15 Joseph Crehan (age 82), who played Commissioner Salisbury the movie in episode 702- THE BRUTE MAN.

04/17 Mario Serandrei (age 58), editor for the movies in episodes 408- HERCULES UNCHAINED and 502- HERCULES.

04/19 Paul Palmentola (age 78), art director of the movies in episodes 507- I ACCUSE MY PARENTS and 522- TEEN-AGE CRIME WAVE.

05/21 Pat O'Malley (age 75), who played an engineer in the season two serial THE PHANTOM CREEPS.

06/10 Ned LeFevre (age 54), who played a newscaster in the movie in episode 801- REVENGE OF THE CREATURE and an announcer in the movie in episode 804- THE DEADLY MANTIS.

Date in July unknown Madge Cleveland (age 92), who played an old frump in the movie in episode 409- THE INDESTRUCTIBLE MAN.

07/05 John P. Fulton (age 63), who did the special effects for the movie in episode 906- THE SPACE CHILDREN.

07/06 Anne Nagel (age 50), who played Lenora Cameron in the movie in episode 103- THE MAD MONSTER.

08/04 Howard Jackson (age 66), musical score composer for the short THE DAYS OF OUR YEARS, shown in episode 623- THE AMAZING TRANSPARENT MAN.

08/15 Jack Mather (age 58), who played an officer in the movie in episode 804- THE DEADLY MANTIS.

08/23 Francis X. Bushman (age 83), who was the narrator in the movie in episode 524- 12 TO THE MOON and played Sesom in the movie in episode 902- THE PHANTOM PLANET.

09/09 Nestor Paiva (age 61), who played Lucas the greasy skipper in the movie in episode 801- REVENGE OF THE CREATURE and was also memorable as "The Load" in the movie in episode 803- THE MOLE PEOPLE.

09/17 Larry Butterworth (age 46), makeup artist for the movie in episode 311- IT CONQUERED THE WORLD.

10/16 John Reynolds (age 25, suicide), who played Torgo in the movie in episode 424- MANOS, THE HANDS OF FATE.

11/15 William Haade (age 63), who played Rocky Rockford in the movie in episode 611- LAST OF THE WILD HORSES.
